title: 849. Best & Worst Case Rookie Scenarios + Rookie Projections
itunes:title: 849. Best & Worst Case Rookie Scenarios + Rookie Projections
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a new episode of Move the Sticks. To start off, the guys give best and worst case scenarios for a bunch of the rookies across the league, as well as rookie projections for this season. Then, the duo look at the quarterback battle in Pittsburgh between Mitchell Trubisky and Kenny Pickett.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
